queue
Class Queue

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--queue.Queue
public class Queue
extends java.lang.Object

Simple implementation of a queue ADT. Only the methods necessary by the "catch-the-nut" game are provided.

This queue supports only single threaded accesses (note that the game in which it is used is multithreaded).
